Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.48,0:00:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想打從心裡大叫一句\N好想快點見到妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.33,0:00:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信總有一天\N一定能相遇相知永結連理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.17,0:00:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起步走出\N希望妳能追著我的背影而來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.49,0:00:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我孤單一人只為等候妳的到來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.64,0:01:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,落英繽紛的春日午後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.58,0:01:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我將祈禱轉為誓言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.75,0:01:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但願妳不會忘記最重要的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.86,0:01:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永遠閃亮動人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.07,0:01:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,部長,店裡打烊了之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.58,0:01:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看這封信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.83,0:01:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給部長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.49,0:01:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太郎和花子,請你多多照顧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.87,0:02:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,霞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.03,0:02:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小霞那傢伙跟客人跑掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.17,0:02:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下傷腦筋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.24,0:02:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.57,0:02:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小朋友…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.28,0:02:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.61,0:02:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.75,0:02:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這兩個孩子是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.25,0:02:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為出了一點事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.96,0:03:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,給妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.33,0:03:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.54,0:03:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,真是有精神的小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.44,0:03:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個嬰兒哪裡來的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.41,0:03:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.58,0:03:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八成是他的私生子,私生子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.98,0:03:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這兩個都是私生子嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.15,0:03:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人到了走投無路\N什麼事都做得出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.95,0:03:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟五代也是個男人嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.39,0:03:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裕作!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.86,0:03:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你們不要鬧了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.13,0:03:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,對不起,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.60,0:03:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那些叔叔阿姨們不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.56,0:03:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不哭喔,乖喔乖喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.47,0:03:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#82 滿分爸爸!五代的育兒故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.17,0:03:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,酒家小姐跑掉了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.38,0:03:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,這兩個小孩\N今晚先由我照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.98,0:03:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.08,0:04:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真可憐,他們什麼都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.39,0:04:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是母親不回來的話\N那該怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.76,0:04:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去找啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.16,0:04:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裡找?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.76,0:04:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.70,0:04:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這個人做事真是沒計劃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.20,0:04:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬一找不到的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.63,0:04:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個男生會當你們的爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.90,0:04:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-爸爸,爸爸\N-喂…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.94,0:04:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是,明天怎麼辦呢?\N這兩個孩子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.05,0:04:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆留他們在這裡\N直到找到他們的母親為止吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.45,0:04:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.05,0:04:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.69,0:04:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想一直待在這裡嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.36,0:04:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他想籠絡管理員喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.83,0:04:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這小鬼好像蠻精明的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.64,0:04:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別用這種算計世故的看法\N來看這個小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.70,0:05:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,竟然忍心丟下\N這麼可愛的小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.98,0:05:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乖喔乖喔,不哭不哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.25,0:05:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.35,0:05:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這有什麼辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.80,0:05:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好喔好喔,不哭不哭\N好乖好乖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.60,0:05:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乖喔乖喔,不哭不哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.57,0:06:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.34,0:06:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.81,0:06:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上哭了起來是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.01,0:06:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.01,0:06:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.98,0:06:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換我來哄她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.55,0:06:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.75,0:06:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係,讓我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.92,0:06:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乖喔,乖喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.80,0:06:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經睡著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.01,0:06:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才還哭得那麼厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.27,0:06:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是被女生抱\N會覺得比較安心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.07,0:07:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.08,0:07:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.08,0:07:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尿尿了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.92,0:07:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子尿尿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.84,0:07:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就這樣了,辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.37,0:07:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡,我才不好意思呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.74,0:07:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太郎,要乖乖聽大家的話喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.15,0:07:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.12,0:07:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嬰兒就交給我們照顧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.75,0:07:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是過來人嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.16,0:08:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.29,0:08:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,部長,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.03,0:08:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.13,0:08:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代的麻煩一件接著一件\N也真是夠他累了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.91,0:08:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是,這很像五代的作風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.98,0:08:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也對啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.52,0:08:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.82,0:08:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.06,0:08:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,五代,這麼早就來了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.00,0:08:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,霞姊有沒有什麼聯絡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.66,0:08:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.27,0:08:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說小霞跑掉了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.71,0:08:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.74,0:08:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.11,0:08:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在酒家小姐之間是很出名的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.91,0:08:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每換一家店工作\N就跟店裡的客人私奔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.22,0:09:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.65,0:09:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是她第一次\N拋棄小孩囉?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.12,0:09:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,饒不了她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.76,0:09:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是覺得沒什麼用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.80,0:09:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去小霞的公寓看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.97,0:09:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡,明天過去看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.74,0:09:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.04,0:09:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是難得啊,阿瞬竟然回家來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.01,0:09:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦,一臉悶悶不樂的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.31,0:09:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難得回家一趟,幹嘛擺一張臭臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.78,0:09:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回來得正好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.28,0:09:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是你爸爸公司的\N創立紀念日,剛好放假在家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.72,0:09:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.02,0:09:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.19,0:09:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?這麼正經
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.90,0:09:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你們見見某個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.00,0:09:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,見某個人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.10,0:09:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是為了什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.87,0:09:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為,我想結婚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.18,0:10:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是九条明日菜小姐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.11,0:10:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前幾天才見過不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.48,0:10:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是另一位小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.25,0:10:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟明日菜小姐的婚事\N是叔叔擅自牽線的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.09,0:10:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊\N我覺得那位小姐不錯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.33,0:10:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是認真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.03,0:10:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管誰怎麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.30,0:10:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算要反對\N也請見過本人再說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.80,0:10:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那要什麼時候?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.40,0:10:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,見面的日子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.58,0:10:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們願意見她嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.88,0:10:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然願意啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.82,0:10:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次是怎麼樣的小姐呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.65,0:10:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,好期待喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.39,0:10:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-真的好令人期待喔\N-就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.22,0:10:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然說得這麼輕鬆…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.36,0:10:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我應該早點說才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.54,0:11:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,這裡是千草家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.64,0:11:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,三鷹先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.61,0:11:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伯母您好,突然打電話給您\N是這樣的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.08,0:11:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要跟你爸媽一起吃飯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.22,0:11:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊,樂意之至
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.02,0:11:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,響子那邊\N就由我來跟她聯絡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.32,0:11:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用這樣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.83,0:11:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子由我來聯絡就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.86,0:11:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為如果說是要她去相親\N那孩子就會緊張得要命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.03,0:11:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好,請儘管放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.14,0:11:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會把她帶去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.17,0:11:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題,請包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.17,0:11:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,好,再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.91,0:11:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.35,0:11:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做到這種地步應該沒問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.72,0:11:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子,事到如今不能回頭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.72,0:11:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.72,0:11:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.20,0:12:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然睡得那麼香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.07,0:12:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像母子似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.81,0:12:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這兩個孩子\N知道自己的處境嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.18,0:12:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裕作也真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.77,0:12:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員\N今天我要去霞姊的住處看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.01,0:12:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,如果她在家的話\N何必把孩子交給你照顧呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.01,0:12:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話雖然是這麼說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.15,0:12:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說小霞跑掉了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.12,0:12:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.52,0:12:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在酒家小姐之間是很出名的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.99,0:12:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每換一家店工作\N就跟店裡的客人私奔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.00,0:13:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到她的話\N一定要好好訓她一頓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.54,0:13:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.86,0:13:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,霞姊,霞姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.37,0:13:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,霞姊,妳不在家嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.98,0:13:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然不可能在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.32,0:14:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在看什麼,你這個大色狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.73,0:14:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,霞姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.00,0:14:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,部長,你在這裡幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.90,0:14:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把…把水關掉好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.11,0:14:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起喔,部長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.61,0:14:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的嚇了一大跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.35,0:14:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嚇了一大跳的人是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.03,0:14:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不是跟客人私奔了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.73,0:14:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣嘛\N先來喝一杯吧,部長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.24,0:14:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.11,0:15:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛洗完澡喝啤酒最棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.45,0:15:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧,霞姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.15,0:15:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.15,0:15:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去我住的地方,孩子們都在等妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.59,0:15:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.10,0:15:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳有沒有在聽?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.36,0:15:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫我帶孩子們的換洗衣服去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.33,0:15:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫妳帶去?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.17,0:15:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.20,0:15:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我接下來得出門旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.11,0:15:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳到底在想什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.58,0:15:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個禮拜,請等我一個禮拜\N部長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.58,0:15:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法原諒\N妳這樣也算是母親嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.86,0:15:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,部長\N你願意跟我結婚嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.56,0:15:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我要跟妳結婚?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.93,0:15:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辦不到吧,辦不到吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.20,0:15:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,花子妳怎麼啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.94,0:16:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是怪了,已經給她喝過奶了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.34,0:16:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尿片也沒溼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.58,0:16:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這該怎麼辦呢?\N她一直哭個不停耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.55,0:16:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她才剛開始哭而已吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.38,0:16:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是傷腦筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.05,0:16:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳太緊張了啦,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.25,0:16:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不倒翁,不倒翁,鴨子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.66,0:16:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在找願意當\N這兩個孩子父親的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.10,0:16:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次的男人\N只要再加把勁就成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.53,0:16:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要趁這一個禮拜的旅行搞定他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.50,0:16:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在孩子們需要的是\N當母親的妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.84,0:16:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子們都很諒解我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.21,0:16:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們怎麼會懂啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.91,0:16:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下哦\N我回一下呼叫器的電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.06,0:16:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,媽媽?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.23,0:17:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯,太郎,怎麼啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.54,0:17:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花子哭個不停?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.31,0:17:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,這種時候啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.48,0:17:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把她抱直,輕輕拍她的背
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.45,0:17:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把她抱直,像這樣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.49,0:17:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.89,0:17:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個都好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.23,0:17:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再過一個禮拜\N就去接你們回來喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.36,0:17:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,我們很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.16,0:17:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太郎,讓我講一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.87,0:17:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,妳是孩子的媽媽嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.84,0:17:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,妳是部長公寓的管理員啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.14,0:17:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次實在太給你們添麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.98,0:17:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫他來聽電話喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.85,0:17:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代?到底是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.22,0:17:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之我現在要把孩子的媽\N帶回去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.66,0:18:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別跑!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.53,0:18:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,出了什麼事?五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.63,0:18:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.14,0:18:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,霞姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.53,0:18:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,霞姊,請等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.26,0:18:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,部長,幫我把門窗關好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.90,0:18:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,霞姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.30,0:18:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個禮拜後,我一定會回來的\N孩子們拜託你照顧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.27,0:18:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,霞姊,請等等我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.25,0:18:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,霞姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.20,0:19:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.23,0:19:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被她逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.83,0:19:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下該怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.97,0:19:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是傷腦筋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.97,0:19:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣根本沒辦法開宴會嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.84,0:19:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們真是夠了\N你們到底在擔心什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.28,0:19:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開宴會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.25,0:19:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子真開朗啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.83,0:19:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.89,0:19:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.16,0:19:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太郎都這麼說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.90,0:19:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝個痛快吧,喝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.17,0:19:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好耶,喝吧喝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.78,0:20:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們走了,不好意思\N花子拜託妳照顧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.78,0:20:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,你們慢慢洗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.12,0:20:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.56,0:20:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.93,0:20:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代不用去酒家上班嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.40,0:20:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說今天休假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.60,0:20:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.64,0:20:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惜什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.10,0:20:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.85,0:20:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,我是音無…哦,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.35,0:20:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,響子,是這樣的\N這個星期六妳有空嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.52,0:20:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的生日?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.16,0:20:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要去飯店吃飯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.62,0:20:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾出去吃頓飯有什麼關係\N孝順一下爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.63,0:20:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-沒問題吧?\N-嗯,是可以啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.40,0:20:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,下午三點見\N沒問題吧,響子,不要忘了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.01,0:21:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得爸爸的生日應該是九月…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.32,0:21:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,三鷹先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.52,0:21:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,她願意來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.12,0:21:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,她開心得要命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.69,0:21:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,星期六下午三點,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.06,0:21:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和我爸媽都很期待與你們見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.97,0:21:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星期六,下午三點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.38,0:21:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了,麥肯諾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.16,0:22:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心點,小心點\N打得太兇小心掉下來喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.54,0:22:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子真是無憂無慮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.69,0:22:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太郎,你不會寂寞嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.99,0:22:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會,一點都不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.12,0:22:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望媽媽能早點回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.86,0:22:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽跟星星說好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.06,0:22:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟星星?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.10,0:22:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.48,0:22:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太郎,聽著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.31,0:22:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對那顆星星發誓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.85,0:22:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個禮拜後我一定回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.22,0:22:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確像霞姊會做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.02,0:23:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊,你很相信媽媽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.70,0:23:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯,不可以對星星說謊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.50,0:23:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她一定會回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.48,0:23:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,掉下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.85,0:23:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,你們在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.35,0:23:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裕作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.92,0:23:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天上有什麼嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.03,0:23:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幽浮嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.61,0:23:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?響子跟三鷹?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.88,0:23:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是他們兩家人見面吃飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.88,0:23:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後兩人去看得見港灣的旅館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.01,0:23:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可非比尋常啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.72,0:24:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣…響子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.72,0:24:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回\N『追到橫濱響子逃走了!』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.82,0:24:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女人對浪漫氣氛很沒輒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.93,0:24:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin the night
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.70,0:24:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin your love
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.87,0:24:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳該知道這不是擦身而過的戀情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.87,0:24:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親吻也是…woo
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.08,0:24:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳比我想像中冷淡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.19,0:24:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡一個人獨處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:42.86,0:24:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沉默不語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:47.70,0:24:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要逞強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:51.44,0:24:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這燭火依偎著的夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:01.68,0:25:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凝視著妳的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:08.62,0:25:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,試著將至今的謊言吹熄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:16.46,0:25:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin the night
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:20.16,0:25:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin your love
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:23.27,0:25:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自我陶醉故弄玄虛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:27.61,0:25:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我行不通…woo
